subproject.description: The objectives of the project are to facilitate and account for the access of goods and construction materials into the Gaza Strip for UNDP projects. In addition, to demonstrate that the imported materials are adequately used for the projects they were intended for. Besides, to strengthen UNDP access and monitoring capacity. Also, to support key rehabilitation activities which are underway. As well as to ensure transparency for the effective use of construction materials for better working relationships with associated parties and stakeholders.
subproject.title: Access Coordination and Monito
